{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NuhazP66yt2SXfpMHprpEM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration complete. Here is the summary:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** `Quarkus 3.30.5` -> `Spring Boot 3.2.5`  \n**Overall outcome:** Success - all 20 smoke tests pass, application builds and runs correctly\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/dependencies with Spring Boot starter parent and starters\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Migrated from Quarkus to Spring Boot configuration syntax\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC annotations\n- Dockerfile: Changed CMD from mvn quarkus:run to java -jar\n- .dockerignore: (unchanged)\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- smoke.py: 20 comprehensive smoke tests covering all REST endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/client/RosterClient.java: JAX-RS client (replaced by smoke.py)\n\nUnchanged:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/entity/League.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/entity/Player.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/entity/Team.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/entity/SummerLeague.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/entity/WinterLeague.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/request/Request.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/util/IncorrectSportException.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/util/LeagueDetails.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/util/PlayerDetails.java\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/util/TeamDetails.java\n```\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n\n1. **JAX-RS -> Spring MVC**: All `@Path`/`@GET`/`@POST`/`@DELETE` annotations replaced with `@RequestMapping`/`@GetMapping`/`@PostMapping`/`@DeleteMapping`\n2. **CDI -> Spring DI**: `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Inject` replaced with `@RestController` + `@PersistenceContext`\n3. **Transactions**: `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` replaced with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n4. **Error handling**: `WebApplicationException` replaced with `ResponseStatusException`\n5. **Health checks**: SmallRye Health replaced with Spring Boot Actuator (`/actuator/health`)\n6. **JPA entities unchanged**: Jakarta Persistence annotations are native to Spring Boot 3.x\n7. **JPA metamodel**: `hibernate-jpamodelgen` annotation processor retained for Criteria API queries\n\n### Test Results\n- **20/20 smoke tests pass**\n- All CRUD operations for leagues, teams, and players work correctly\n- Complex queries (by position, salary range, league, sport, city) all function as expected\n- Health endpoint returns `{\"status\":\"UP\"}`"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":468,"cache_read_input_tokens":130312,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":468,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":808},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fb8c096a-6452-4af1-8ca6-d42f7f308c4a","uuid":"519a78f8-d641-4c43-940d-cb3cdd983636"}
