 + `@Inject` replaced with `@RestController` + `@PersistenceContext`\n3. **Transactions**: `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` replaced with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n4. **Error handling**: `WebApplicationException` replaced with `ResponseStatusException`\n5. **Health checks**: SmallRye Health replaced with Spring Boot Actuator (`/actuator/health`)\n6. **JPA entities unchanged**: Jakarta Persistence annotations are native to Spring Boot 3.x\n7. **JPA metamodel**: `hibernate-jpamodelgen` annotation processor retained for Criteria API queries\n\n### Test Results\n- **20/20 smoke tests pass**\n- All CRUD operations for leagues, teams, and players work correctly\n- Complex queries (by position, salary range, league, sport, city) all function as expected\n- Health endpoint returns `{\"status\":\"UP\"}`","session_id":"fb8c096a-6452-4af1-8ca6-d42f7f308c4a","total_cost_usd":12.890090209999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":14600,"cache_creation_input_tokens":118337,"cache_read_input_tokens":5273485,"output_tokens":32000,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":118337}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":98339,"outputTokens":6294,"cacheReadInputTokens":163997,"cacheCreationInputTokens":20112,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.13707896000000006,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":515,"outputTokens":228,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.004965000000000001,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":14600,"outputTokens":32000,"cacheReadInputTokens":5273485,"cacheCreationInputTokens":118337,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":12.748046250000003,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"fdfd4bfb-6790-4e7d-9c5e-956cb7302129"}
